  "title": "Cobblemon: Create Industries (3D Production Models)",
  "description": "Create + Cobblemon : 3D Production of Balls, Candy, Mochi's.",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><strong>Cobblemon: Create Industries &ndash; A Cobblemon &amp; Create Integration Mod</strong></span></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Balls 3D Models</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_7103db05-076d-4ae7-a546-39b6ce15ee20.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"399\"></h1>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><strong>Please comment new things for this mod or ideas for new mods and addons, I'll be creating these mods as much as possible. I hope you enjoy.<br><br></strong></span></h3>\n<hr>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>Cobblemon: Create Industries</strong> is a mod that brings together the advanced automation of the <em>Create</em> mod with the Pok&eacute;mon-catching experience of <em>Cobblemon</em>. The goal is to allow players to craft key Cobblemon items using Create&rsquo;s powerful mechanical systems!</span></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><strong>Current Features:<br><br></strong></span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>◽ Crafting of Standard Pok&eacute; Balls:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;All standard Pok&eacute; Balls 3D can now be manufactured using Create&rsquo;s machinery and automation.<br></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>◽ Crafting of Ancient Pok&eacute; Balls:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ancient Pok&eacute; Balls from Cobblemon are also available to be crafted in a more technical and immersive way.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #1f1f1f;\"><strong>◽ Pok&eacute;mon Candies:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Create various types of candies to feed, boost, and care for your Pok&eacute;mon using mechanical processes</strong></span></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h3>\n<hr>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Craft Balls</h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_1107a900-da72-4bf9-8a6c-ab86bc819715.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_30454f16-19b8-4e55-95e4-2f9af6cdbec2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_c6c57e03-dd92-49aa-a52f-671e7e446cfb.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_5ae3858d-7d27-4cde-af0a-7c5e4667ae9a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Craft Candy</h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_36dfef0e-9dd7-4e6c-afc1-87f358444ab9.png\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_db06a442-67a4-402a-8bb6-f1621a4d284b.png\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_9585ef51-399d-41a7-8010-20e48a6c9be9.png\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1263211/description_a6418073-c49a-45c5-9de6-e6b82f441f15.png\" width=\"362\" height=\"298\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
